Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.42,0:00:03.35,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really need to dress up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:04.40,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:08.78,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be meeting with a very important trading partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:10.04,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:12.24,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,He sent you that amazing love letter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:13.66,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:15.57,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it was full of passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.80,0:00:17.61,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell her that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:18.99,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,You two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:21.79,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:22.54,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:23.92,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:25.73,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:27.52,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:27.90,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}{First white frame}
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.95,0:00:42.91,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I want to be annoying for you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.91,0:00:45.87,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I don't mind being conceited
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.87,0:00:49.92,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Hide a tree in a forest, they say
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.34,0:00:54.34,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}It started with a little mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.34,0:00:57.43,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Let's redo our meeting from there
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.43,0:01:01.89,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Let's oppose the strand of time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.64,0:01:07.85,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Strength alone is no weapon
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.94,0:01:15.78,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}You taught me that just now
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.03,0:01:21.24,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I want to show you what lies
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.24,0:01:27.75,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}beyond these days
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.75,0:01:30.21,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}The wind is strong
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.21,0:01:33.42,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I'm sure you know that too
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.42,0:01:38.22,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I can't fly
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.09,0:01:45.02,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Sharing makes you dependant
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.02,0:01:48.31,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Now, take my hand
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.31,0:01:50.77,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Hold it tight
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.77,0:01:54.94,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Now...
