Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:02.68,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:06.98,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who falls that easily has no right to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.19,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Summer's finally here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.37,0:02:10.53,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:13.23,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The courtyard will only continue to heat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:15.03,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,When she first arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and learned that the Hero was nowhere to be found,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:21.48,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,she went on a rampage, like a badger with an arrow in its butt.{the arrow from the first episode finds its mark}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:33.59,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hold this with both hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:35.60,Default,Ss,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:36.98,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:38.17,Default,Ss,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.02,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Hero left,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you haven't put any thought into picking your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:52.16,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.59,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,He's just on a business trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:56.28,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:59.86,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't abandoned you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:00.78,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:03.28,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,But today, you look lovely, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:04.41,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:07.89,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Looking good is an important part of negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:11.42,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't this a little over the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.05,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's cut so low...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:16.09,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ashamed of your ugly, useless flesh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.92,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:21.63,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The Knight and the villagers told me it looks wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:25.01,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,But without a motherly personality to back it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.93,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,it's just useless flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.27,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty harsh today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:34.52,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,If you were facing a nobleman or a soldier, you could simply summon the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:38.07,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,But since you're meeting with Alliance merchants,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.28,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,you'll have to handle this on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:43.49,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Not being able to help makes me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:47.91,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,If we're lucky, the Hero will return in time for the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:51.20,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Even if things go bad, we can run.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.58,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to rely on the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:57.55,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that men feel uneasy around strong women.{I AM A STRONG, INDEPENDENT DEMON KING WHO DON'T NEED NO MAN}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.92,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Miss,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.93,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,your boobs look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.51,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait until the dress is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.27,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what kind of person will be waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.65,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,If things go bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:20.28,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,we follow the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:22.82,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:25.00,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,it's time to get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:25.70,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:30.08,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,The Horror Ghosts and Night Ghosts are already in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:32.40,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:40.55,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shocked to meet such a beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:46.84,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,It appears your beauty shines as brightly as your wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:49.61,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,These gaudy clothes are
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a silly woman's attempt to improve her negotiating position.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:56.02,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll laugh and forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:05:00.69,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I did expect to see you sooner, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.51,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:04.40,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,This matter is of grave importance to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:10.03,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of preparation was required to allow someone as low a rank as I am to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.31,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.07,0:05:14.54,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Then let us begin negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.13,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,What
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.00,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.72,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anything like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:25.24,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,This plant is called corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.46,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's an annual plant,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:32.81,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,most importantly characterized by its ability to flourish with minimal water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:35.43,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It requires a temperature of thirty degrees to bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:37.23,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Fairly high...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.52,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:41.47,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,So it's perfect for the wilds of the Central Nations, which have,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until now, been unsuited to raising crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:48.78,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That area is enormous...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:50.74,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Merchant,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this could be bigger business than you've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:58.25,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You could send men out to settle in the empty wilderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.55,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It would take effort and capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but a large-scale harvesting operation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on well-organized land would result in the most efficient
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and productive farms known to man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.35,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,And the villages you found
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will become a massive market, completely under Alliance control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:17.48,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You'd have new customers who require more goods than just corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wood, salt, iron, cloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you can sell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:29.32,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,So what you're trying to sell us isn't a product
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.23,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,or a method of harvesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:32.99,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,It's a new idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:35.13,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Can you even sell something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.54,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,But are you certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.56,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Once we have this knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can advance the plan without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.97,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,What's in it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:48.76,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,What do {\i1}you{\i0} want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:51.30,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,A swift end to the war
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that is neither victory nor defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:56.44,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:07:00.59,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,The war cannot end any way but with our victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:05.31,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The Alliance is the biggest sponsor of the war against the demons, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:07.92,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,We have a duty to give all we can
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the struggle against humanity's enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:13.12,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what you tell people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.33,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,It is what we believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:30.66,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The high and the low, the north and the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:33.84,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Fire and ice. Light and darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:36.14,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,As merchants, isn't it your job to stand as intermediaries,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to negotiate and trade, then reap the benefits?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.89,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a friend of the Alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:43.65,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Or its enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:46.36,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,A trading partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:52.17,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Your words a moment ago were a betrayal of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:54.85,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,And blasphemy in the eyes of the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dreams are like your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red as blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:01.75,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to tread that path alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.50,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,What do you see in the Alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you think we'll help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:16.75,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I believe we all have something to gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:21.72,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That is what we have in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is the second strongest bond between Heaven and Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:32.48,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.14,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:35.98,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:39.95,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,We are merchants before we are human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:44.22,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,We are merchants before we are faithful servants of the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:47.13,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,That is exactly what the Alliance instructs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:48.27,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:51.13,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I value contracts above all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:53.63,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:54.93,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,So do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:56.80,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Let us make one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:00.96,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,A contract that will light the way to our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:19.78,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You had me worried for a moment there, Merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.25,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,I could say the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:24.80,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been so nervous in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:27.68,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,The royal family itself lacks the fire you displayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:31.74,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Let us shake hands to seal the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:37.01,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,When can we get started with the corn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:38.29,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:41.39,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,but I still have several experiments and harvests ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.48,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I should have it ready by next spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:44.64,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,That's plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:48.06,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,I must strengthen my position in the Alliance as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:51.15,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that compass comes in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:53.64,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make good use of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:55.15,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:10:00.25,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,You said having something to gain from one another is the second strongest bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:01.63,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,What is the first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.08,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:04.83,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:11.31,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:13.26,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:14.98,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:18.42,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you've made me feel this way twice in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:20.34,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,You truly are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.91,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Even a child knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:27.18,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Then I suppose I've no choice but to propose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:31.72,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-P-Propose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.28,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Propose marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.48,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.87,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:38.26,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You should be ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:39.28,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:40.63,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:45.44,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,I need a dowry and gifts in order to propose...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.06,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No, I-I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:50.54,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to treat this as a long-term project.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:53.25,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Stubbornness is like decisiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are both a merchant's most important weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:59.22,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No, regardless of how much time you spend, I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.39,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Will we meet again in the capital? Or on a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:03.76,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Let us meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:10.98,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.32,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,May I call you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:20.32,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:22.54,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:26.19,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:27.83,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:29.53,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:32.46,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:35.42,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever heard of the potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:38.30,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Have you tried one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:40.09,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they're excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:43.48,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told a wandering scholar brought them to these lands,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:47.56,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,and the Lakeside Convent is spreading them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:52.08,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,They've offered us a stable source of wheat, pigs, and sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:55.98,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,They're also improving our farming tools and establishing education facilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.02,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,They've created windmills as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.49,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Windmills?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:01.51,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,They're like waterwheels,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they use wind, not water, for power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:08.54,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,If the windmills spread, they'll improve our food situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:10.13,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,since our country lacks good water sources.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the people will no longer have to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:18.63,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,We should just end the war and assist the convent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.78,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,If the war ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the support we receive from the Central Nations will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:28.64,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Our country will not last.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:32.22,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wondered
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why we sent a single man to end the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:39.69,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.65,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,We mustn't be too hasty now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:47.12,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What is this stack of papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.05,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,It's from the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:52.62,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Delivery statements, bills, receipts, specifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:55.36,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you had on your purchase list.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:58.00,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,And this is just twenty percent of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.44,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty percent?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:02.75,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.72,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.64,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have her do them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.40,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:09.97,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:11.48,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:14.25,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's fall already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.77,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:17.06,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's fall already, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:17.98,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:20.73,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Why haven't I heard from him in six months?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:22.67,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my... Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.95,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Stop repeating that in hopes I'll shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.74,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,He could at least send word!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:28.31,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,He has.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:29.20,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:31.54,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,How he saved the fairies...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:34.06,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Or after a battle with the Dragon Archduke,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:38.03,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,the Archduke took a liking to him and offered his daughter in marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:43.28,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Or that the Mage was seen at the Outer Library.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:47.05,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,But that Hero's a virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:50.60,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Virgins express a strong sense of duty in peculiar ways
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.12,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,and tend to be dreamers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:53.71,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:55.64,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That explanation isn't nearly good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:14:00.23,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay angry, those wrinkles will never leave your brow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:08.52,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, I'll take a bite out of the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:09.95,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.78,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.43,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking too much is bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:17.07,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:18.97,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me some tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:30.76,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Her Majesty says she'll take a bite out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:38.23,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You knew I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:40.20,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,A maid's intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.77,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You find me every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:44.44,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have your latest letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.73,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:48.99,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you some tea as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:59.12,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,So not this time either?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:04.51,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,You're avoiding Her Majesty, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:06.71,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,You are, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:15.61,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,I've chosen not to say anything because I didn't feel
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was my place as a servant to ask, but this is going nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:25.23,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell Her Majesty, so if there is a problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:27.08,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:30.32,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Is it what I think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:32.82,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,You were approached by harpy girls at an inn,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:35.83,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,or a translucent slime girl confessed her love to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:40.25,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,or a well-endowed cow girl said you were her groom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:42.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:45.43,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,With your teleportation spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:48.67,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,you could come back weekly, if not daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:56.76,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,But you haven't, and Her Majesty is getting worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:16:00.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that she doesn't need me for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:07.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,When she first ordered me to be hers, in the throne room...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:09.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,She told me I'd see something I'd never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:14.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought I'd use my power to put down the demon rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:17.07,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe even close the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:19.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that was how we'd end the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:23.58,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that's what she meant when she said she wanted my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:27.84,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But she never uses me to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:32.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, she keeps trying to ensure that I never fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:35.64,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's like she cares too much about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.09,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say why, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:43.56,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:45.56,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We made a contract!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:49.13,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,She's mine, and I'm hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:50.73,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To her Majesty, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:55.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.70,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,When I picture my death,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:08.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,all I can see is her face, and she seems on the verge of tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:09.21,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:18.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I guess I'm not much of a Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:22.97,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,As a maid, it isn't my place, but let me say one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:27.02,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,You belong to Her Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:32.53,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you have belongs to my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.58,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:39.35,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Then the hesitation and compassion you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:42.87,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,the wishes you're keeping hidden, and the hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.86,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Your prayers to be with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:48.23,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Even the feelings you have for her that you can't express.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:51.13,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,All of it belongs to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:55.08,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not forget that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:00.60,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.82,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,They say the villagers are going to dance...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:05.11,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Boys and girls together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:06.81,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the New Year's festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:11.83,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the Hero comes back, and our master gets to dance with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:12.82,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:14.48,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:19.16,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,They won't send a Crusade of the Holy Key,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:21.33,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,but they want us to defeat the demons anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:24.04,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,Damn those Centrals!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:28.32,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the Conference of Southern Nations will be opposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:30.04,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,Except for the White Night Country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:35.28,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,They're the sole country that's strengthened their ties to the Central Nations,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.55,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,hoping to become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:40.40,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,And because of them, we're going to have a war!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:43.36,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,And it'll happen on Bright Light Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:46.59,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,The one island the demons have taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:50.01,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,If we were to fight them without entering the Demon World,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.48,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,that would be the one place we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:56.59,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly, they said something about 200 warships and 7,000 soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:19:01.49,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,Throwing that many people into a naval battle is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:06.36,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,If they sink 200 warships, we'd lose all 7,000 men!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:08.47,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:11.35,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,We've no plan, and there's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:15.05,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,But we must wag our tails and commit troops because the Centrals order it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:17.13,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,It's madness!{madness... you say?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:19.26,Default,Ns,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.48,0:19:21.04,Default,Ss,0000,0000,0000,,It's this winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:23.15,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:23.99,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Form up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:25.29,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:27.77,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You seem excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:30.77,Default,Ns,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard the rumors that we're going to war, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.21,Default,Ss,0000,0000,0000,,My blood is pumping!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:36.02,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eyes open and listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:38.99,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Question whether you're certain this is a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:44.84,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You carry the weight of many lives and much wealth,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and not just your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:49.41,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,The demons are evil? And the humans are good?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:51.29,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,In war, that's irrelevant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:54.13,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,There are only winners and losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:57.79,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to war, I won't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.42,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.80,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,But I will not allow you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:04.50,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You are too young and inexperienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:09.74,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,If you die, you'll do it with a stupid expression,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wondering where you went wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:15.60,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,So I won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:18.02,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I told them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:19.52,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:21.34,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I told them all that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:25.82,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I say, I'm just a substitute teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:28.42,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't the right to say anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:30.51,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.16,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.31,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:35.74,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,So I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:40.46,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,want to use my feet... and to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:43.32,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You want to learn to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:44.97,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:48.69,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,But all I do with my students is terrify them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:49.75,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:52.56,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,You're a much better teacher than the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:58.95,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,He's too vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:00.20,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:04.37,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I even doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:08.37,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Because it lets you think he trusts you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:11.18,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:15.50,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:19.50,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,That's what let you make that crystal greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:22.16,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,That shiny, glittering building?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:26.01,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,But after building that, the convent's coffers are empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:28.55,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:31.07,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,You seem happy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:35.12,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, you seem like the Head Maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:36.32,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:37.92,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:39.52,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:42.55,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I can read now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:44.03,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,I've learned arithmetic,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:46.53,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,and I can do many things now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:49.03,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,The villagers are very kind to me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:52.41,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:55.83,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.39,0:22:03.79,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really human now?
